Valeska Suratt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Valeska_Suratt 0 Valeska Suratt (June 28, 1882 – July 2, 1962) was an American stage and silent film actress. Over the course of her career, Surratt appeared in 11 silent films all of which are now lost. Valeska_Suratt ( June_28_,_1882 – July_2_,_1962 ) was an_American_stage and silent_film_actress .
